Title: Hack to the Future - NDC Sydney 2020 | Software Developers Conference
Description: Infosec is a continual game of one-upmanship; we build a defence and someone breaks it so we build another one then they break that and the cycle continues. Because of this, the security controls we have at our disposal are rapidly changing and the ones we used yesterday are very often useless today.

Title: Blazor in more depth - NDC Sydney 2020 | Software Developers Conference
Description: In this talk, Blazor's two architects will take you deeper into the framework, showing a range of more advanced features and their internal workings. We'll dig into server-side Blazor and how we built the SignalR-based mechanism for efficiently streaming UI updates, as well as authorization in Blazor WebAssembly, and more.
